# This configuration is based on jedi_lfric_tests: forecast_nwp_gal9-C12
# It is a direct copy from:
#   run_jedi_lfric_tests_forecast_nwp_gal9-C12_azspice_gnu_fast-debug-64bit
# Created as part of lfric_apps #512
# The "spec" directory is copied from the build:
# <cylc-run-dir>/share/source/socrates/data/spectra/ga9
